   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>To Aurelius Chrestos, strategos [of the Arsinoite nome], from Aurelius Kasios, son of Pelagios, and [Aurelius - - -, son of - - -], both comarchs of the village [of Karanis. We submit] and report at our own [risk] the persons mentioned [below], since they are men of property and qualified [- - -]</ab>
